# Sample HTTP Requests

# cURL POST Example
# curl -d “param1=value1&param2=value2” -H “Content-Type: application/json” -X POST http://localhost:3000/data

# HTTPie POST Example
# http POST http://localhost:3000/data ‘param1=value1’ ‘param2=value2’

### GET Request with Query Parameters

GET https://api.example.com/posts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer your_access_token
Accept: application/json

?limit=10
&offset=0
&category=technology

### POST Request with JSON Body

POST https://api.example.com/posts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer your_access_token

{
  "title": "New Post",
  "content": "This is a sample post.",
  "category": "technology"
}

### PUT Request with JSON Body

PUT https://api.example.com/posts/123
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer your_access_token

{
  "title": "Updated Post Title"
}

### DELETE Request

DELETE https://api.example.com/posts/123
Authorization: Bearer your_access_token

### GET Request with Headers

GET https://api.example.com/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer your_access_token
Accept: application/json

### POST Request with Form Data

POST https://api.example.com/upload
Authorization: Bearer your_access_token
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

[Binary Data]

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### PATCH Request with JSON Body

PATCH https://api.example.com/user/settings
Authorization: Bearer your_access_token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notifications": true,
  "theme": "dark"
}
